# Request form (CTA) — server-side only; set in the Vercel project (not committed).
# The recipient address is never in client code or the repo (masked).
#
# Option A — Web3Forms (recommended; no account, key emailed instantly):
#   Get a free key: enter the owner's email at https://web3forms.com → copy the
#   access key from the email. The key maps to that address on Web3Forms' side,
#   so the email itself never appears anywhere here.
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# Option B — Resend (alternative):
#   RESEND_API_KEY=
#   REQUEST_TO_EMAIL=owner@example.com
#   REQUEST_FROM_EMAIL=ESG Tracker <no-reply@pris.la>   # optional
